<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to EssyKart</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .message {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .activation-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .instructions {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .contact {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333333;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to EssyKart</h1>
        <div class="message">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with us. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <h2 class="activation-code"><%= code %></h2>
            <p class="instructions">Please enter this code on the activation page within 5 minutes.</p>
            <p class="instructions">If you did not register your email with EssyKart, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@essykart.com">support@essykart.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2024 EssyKart. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
